flowchart TB
    A[Start Watch Mode] --> B[Initial Full Render]
    B --> C[Monitor File Changes<br/>chokidar]
    C --> D{File Changed?}
    D -->|Yes| E[Debounce 200ms]
    E --> F[Re-render Changed File]
    F --> G{Render OK?}
    G -->|Yes| H[Update Manifest]
    G -->|No| I[Preserve Existing Output<br/>Log Error]
    H --> C
    I --> C
    D -->|Ctrl+C| J[Dispose Browser Pool]
